snippet.title: Fish Jelly Film Reviews
snippet.description:
We spoil movies. Why watch trailer reactions when you can get the full lowdown here?

Gay homosexuals Nick and Joseph give their take on upcoming theatrical releases and select Blu-ray restorations. Their videos look at cinema from a queer and racially aware perspective. 

Nick and Joseph have been married since 2008. They may seem like they don't get along, but they are very much in love.

Don't forget to checkout our podcast (links below)!
